    <h1 class="reveal d1">People called me a light my whole life.<br/><em>I finally found the source.</em></h1>
    <p class="reveal d2">A little girl from Nepal who grew up worshipping Hindu gods encountered Jesus for the first time at 24 and was never the same again.</p>
  </section>

