        <h2>He used my pain<br/>to <em>heal others.</em></h2>
        <p>After that encounter I felt a nudge to share devotional love notes in the voice of God on social media. I didn't feel ready. I was still healing. But I had a new fire and I said yes. Messages started pouring in from people saying God was speaking to them. That became the Love Notes from God series and eventually Forever Yours.</p>
        <p>My name is Rose. My mom's name was Renuu. Rose Renuu is my way of honoring her and carrying her with me. Today I live in freedom. No more guilt, shame, bitterness, or hiding. If he can turn my story around he can do the same for you.</p>
        <p class="closing-sig">Rose Renuu</p>
